sentence: "why do i want to go into the stem field?"when i was younger, the desire to go into the stem field was largely influenced by my parents and their dreams after immigrating here from bangladesh.
phrase: ["When I was younger, the desire to go into the STEM field was largely influenced by my parents and their dreams after immigrating here from Bangladesh. All throughout K12th grade I knew in my mind that I wanted to do STEM as a way to try to accomplish one of my loving parents' dreams that they sacrificed so much for.I was later diagnosed with ADD, and to me it didn't feel any different knowing what I had or not, I still wanted to accomplish my parents dream no matter what it took.I genuinely want to become a great mechanical engineer for myself, not for my parents, and I want to become a person who can solve problems no matter how challenging, but I have to first overcome the challenge of graduating."]
